          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Cyber Vulnerability Disclosure Reporting Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to submit a report describing the policies and procedures developed to coordinate the disclosure of cyber vulnerabilities. The report shall describe instances&nbsp;when such policies and procedures were used to disclose cyber vulnerabilities in the previous year. Further, the report shall&nbsp;mention the degree to which the disclosed information was acted upon by stakeholders. </p>]]></text>
